REFACTOR

I want to split the views folder into dirs, and pull any generic
code into a lib folder. So, code that doesn't directly express
concepts native to the filtered_search app should be pulled out,
and what remains should inherit from it. This is already the
case with event_layout and accordion_view, but some other classes
such as "paginated_collection_view" could probably use some loving.

views:
    lib
        event_layout.js
        accordion_item_view.js // should express that these are layouts now
        relational_accordion_item_view.js

        accordion_view.js // this is not a layout

    filtered_search
        search_widgets_layout.js

        paginated_collection
            paginated_collection_view.js // descends from accordion_view

            structure
                structure_view.js // this is a layout now, descends from relational_accordion_item_view

                relations
                    comment_view.js
                    course_view.js
                    courses_collection_view.js
                    media_view.js
                    medias_collection_view.js

            filters
                categorical_filter_view.js
                subject_filter_view.js
                location_filter_view.js
                pagination_tool_view.js
                result_summary_view.js

        map
            google_maps_view.js
            structure_marker_view.js

templates:
    filtered_search
        search_widgets_layout_view.jst.hbs.erb

        paginated_collection
            paginated_collection_view.jst.hbs

            structure
                structure_view.jst.hbs

